		'The number of variables is automatically read based on the variable name, so you need to be sure they are named correctly in the SAV data
'------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------'
'------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------'
'------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------'			
		
